Net::PDSH

Copyright (c) 2015 Aditya Pandit
All rights reserved.
This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it under
the same terms as Perl itself.

This module implements a Perl interface to pdsh.  It is a simple wrapper around
the system `pdsh' command. 

To install:
        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test # nothing substantial yet
        make install

Documentation will then be available via `man Net:PDSH' or `perldoc Net::PDSH'

